Class SeniorSquad

java.lang.Object
com.application.simplyrugby.Model.SeniorSquad
All Implemented Interfaces:
Squad
public class SeniorSquad extends Object implements Squad
This is the class to define a Senior Squad.
it will take 15 players and use an ArrayList to store them.
